  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at the 11th Level, you being to outfit your tools with better tools.</p><p>You can select one Scientific Ninja Tool of Creation Point Cost 8 or lower.</p><p>The selected tool is then attached to one weapon or armor of your choice.</p><p>Twice per long rest the holder of this weapon or wearer of the armor can use the tool, as if it was wielded by you, at no chakra cost.</p><p>You can have anumber of Infused Tools equal to your Intelligence modifer.</p><p>During a Long rest you can switch the Scientific Ninja Tool, or reattach it to a new weapon or armor.</p><p></p>",
